                      "description": "Default Time To Live (TTL) of the [Zone](#tag/zones).\n\nMust be in between 60s and 2147483647s.\n\nThis TTL is used for [RRSets](#tag/zone-rrsets) that do not explicitly define a TTL.\n",
                      "type": "integer",
                      "default": 3600,
                      "minimum": 60,
                      "maximum": 2147483647,
